                            <comment id="15614094" author="huxi_2b" created="Fri, 28 Oct 2016 02:53:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;MirrorMakerOldConsumer employs TopicFilter which replaces all commas with &apos;|&apos; during the initialization, while MirrorMakerNewConsumer only receives Options&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;String&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; as the white list which means a strictly valid regular expression should be specified here. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
